name: NumRand
0:
”Alexa, ask Num Rand for a number between one and ten.”
”Give me a number between three and twenty.”
”I would like a number between forty and two.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: num rand
des: Num Rand will give you a random number within a given range. Ask it for a number between two integers, and it'll generate a new random number, inclusive of the two you gave it.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
